<h3><span class="name western">Bruce Y Lee</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>PHICOR (Public Health Informatics Computational Operations Research), City University of New York, New York, New York, (previously at Johns Hopkins University, Baltimore, MD)</div>
