<div class="d-panels font-secondary-light">
<div id="aip_a" class="d-panel p" style="display: none">
<div class="p" id="A1">
<sup>1</sup>PHICOR (Public Health Informatics Computational Operations Research), City University of New York, New York, New York, (previously at Johns Hopkins University, Baltimore, MD)</div>
<div id="A2">
<sup>2</sup>Department of Pediatrics, Stanford University, Stanford, CA</div>
